subject: Session Feedback
response_header: Here is the list of responses that you have submitted, you can edit any response before submitting it.
retry_prompt: Please choose one option for the above question
I would request you to please select an option for the above question
I am sorry but I did not understand that. I need you to select one of the options above
retry_command_prompt: This is not correct command. Please enter the valid command
This is incorrect command, type 'help' to see all available commands
This is invalid question, please type correct command.
session_reset_msg: I have lost my memory (morningafter) please type '**start**' to start the feedback again
not_started_msg: Hey (wait)! You have not started filling the feedback yet. Please give all responses before submitting the feedback.
help_msg:
* If you want to edit any response type 'edit_question_number'. Example- **edit_4** 
 * if you want to submit response type **'submit'** 
 * If you want to reset all responses type **'reset'** 
 * If you want to check all available commands type **'help'**
mail_not_sent_msg: We are not able to send your response to TM team. Please contact to support.
mail_sent_msg: We have sent your response to TM team. Thanks for your time.
reason_msg: Can you please write the reason why you don't want to fill the feedback form?
complete_all_ques_msg: Great Job! (clap) You have submitted all the responses successfully and we appreciate this. (y) What would you like to do now?
half_attempt_msg: You have completed almost half of the questions. (kya) baat hai. Here is a (trophy) for you.
error_msg: There is some problem, please try after some time
no_option_found_error: Sorry I couldn't get you. It seems you have entered something else. Can you please try 'help' for how to proceed.
welcome1_msg: You will be presented with a list of questions. Your answer to those questions can help the trainer identify his strengths and improvement areas to serve you better.
welcome2_msg: You can type '**help**' anytime to see all available commands that I can respond to.
welcome3_msg: **I will help you in providing the feedback for the training** (wave)
feedback_fill_msg: You have just attended the session. We request you to fill the feedback form ASAP.
choose_start_option: What would you like to do? (** Tip :** *Please select or type the option*)
delete_bot: Bot has been delete from the skype list
